The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Robert J. Patterson, Appellant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed. Counsel’s application to withdraw granted (see, People v Crawford, 71 AD2d 38). (Appeal from judgment of Jefferson County Court, Parker, J.—burglary, second degree.) Present—Dillon, P. J., Doerr, Boomer, Pine and Lawton, JJ.
